## I-001 — Login fails with special characters in password

**Status:** open | **Severity:** high | **Found:** 2025-03-15
**Found by:** user report

**Description:**
Login endpoint returns 500 when password contains `&` or `=` characters.
The password is being URL-encoded before hashing, causing a mismatch
with the stored hash.

**Root Cause:** TBD

**Fix:** TBD

---

## I-002 — Dashboard chart flickers on resize

**Status:** open | **Severity:** medium | **Found:** 2025-03-16
**Found by:** self-found during UI audit T005

**Description:**
The revenue chart on the dashboard re-renders completely on every
window resize event instead of debouncing. Causes visible flicker
on slower machines.

**Root Cause:** Missing debounce on resize observer in ChartContainer.tsx

**Fix:** TBD

---

